_sText:
zm_airport_panic_bobpoblo

Zombies have attacked the local city and some residents have taken hold inside the airport, get ready the zombies are coming!


- 64 Spawns
- 3d Skybox
- Cubemaps
- Optimized for better FPS
- Plenty of secret spots
- Overview radar map
- Buy Zones

Secret spots include: vents, illusionary walls, teleport locations and breakable walls.

Many things have been changed and added into this final version, a few things include:
You cannot exploit the elevator anymore. 
The map’s file size has been cut in half.  
Added some teleports and connector vents to speed up getting around the map.
And many more changes that I won’t list.

This is the final version, please enjoy, comment and rate!
